description: Vegetable Nilaga is a Filipino soup 🍲 filled with hearty ingredients like squash, potatoes, carrots, corn, green beans, as well as leafy greens like Napa cabbage, cabbage, and bok choy. It also has meaty and chewy tremelle and sweet saba bananas. Its main base is a good quality vegetable broth and seasonings. It’s a flexible and simple recipe for those looking for vegan and healthy alternative to meat Nilaga soup. For the full post, visit http://www.astigvegan.com/vegan-nilaga-soup/ . Kain na, let’s eat!
